    <article>
        <p>Join us the first Saturday of every month for boardgames at <img src="https://maps.app.goo.gl/phk91LZGjg435oqg8" alt="Union Square Bar And Grill"> at 9pm</p>
<p>We now have a website: <a href="https://robkohr.com/articles/longview-boardgamers">https://robkohr.com/articles/longview-boardgamers</a></p>
<p>If you wanna get all social:</p>
<ul>
<li>There is a facebook group here: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/603728688043181">https://www.facebook.com/groups/603728688043181</a></li>
<li>And a meetup group here: <a href="https://www.meetup.com/longview-kelso-cowlitz-county-board-games-meetup-group/discussions/">https://www.meetup.com/longview-kelso-cowlitz-county-board-games-meetup-group/discussions/</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Primarily, I will be using this email group for communications, so sign up there:</p>
<p><a href="https://groups.io/g/Longview-Washington-Boardgamers">https://groups.io/g/Longview-Washington-Boardgamers</a></p>
